messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Looking for a prayer against masturbation

I understand that you are seeking a prayer against masturbation. Here is a prayer that you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I come before your throne today through the blood of Jesus Christ. I confess my struggle with the sin of masturbation and ask for your forgiveness and cleansing. I renounce this sinful behavior and ask for your strength to overcome it. I break all curses of lust and impurity in the name of Jesus Christ. I command all spirits of lust and perversion to leave me in the name of Jesus. I present my body to you as a living sacrifice, and I ask for your help to live a life of purity and holiness. Thank you, Lord, for your forgiveness and for giving me the strength to overcome this struggle. In Jesus' name, amen."

If you need further assistance or have any other prayer requests, feel free to reach out.
